(2): x + y - 2z = 3 → y = 3 - x + 2z.<br>
Substitusi ke (3): x - (3 - x + 2z) + z = -4 → x - 3 + x - 2z + z = -4 → 2x - 3 - z = -4 → 2x - z = -1 → z = 2x + 1.<br>
Masukkan ke (1): 3x - 2(3 - x + 2(2x + 1)) - 3(2x + 1) = 5 → hasilnya z=-2.`
